  "instructions": [
    "In a small bowl, mix together pistachio paste, cumin powder, coriander powder, salt, and black pepper.",
    "In a clay pot, sauté the sliced red onion in coconut oil until softened.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the lemongrass paste and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the fresh spinach leaves and stir until wilted.",
    "Mix in the pistachio paste mixture.",
    "Steam the mixture in a clay pot for 10 minutes.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh cilantro leaves."
